<ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">This year</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the State Pharmaceutical Administration Bureau</ENAMEX> will evaluate and decide the top <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">50</ENAMEX> enterprises in the pharmaceutical industry according to new criteria .
